OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FLeicester City fans will be hoping new
OL,7,Fmanager Russell Martin has what it
OL,8,Ftakes to get their side promoted to
OL,9,Fthe Championship as he's announced as
OL,10,Fthe new head coach.
OL,12,FIn a statement on Leicester City's
OL,13,Fwebsite, Martin said: "I'm delighted
OL,14,Fto be here and excited to begin
OL,15,Fworking with the players and staff.
OL,17,F"This is a Club with great history,
OL,18,Fstrong support and high expectations,
OL,19,Fand I'm looking forward to getting to
OL,20,Fknow the Club, the city and the
OL,21,Fsupporters.
OL,26,@uD@WOU
