OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,F"My immediate focus is on the team:
OL,7,Fbuilding strong relationships, setting
OL,8,Fclear standards and creating
OL,9,Fperformances that Leicester City
OL,10,Fsupporters can connect with and be
OL,11,Fproud of."
OL,13,FMartin was sacked last season from the
OL,14,FScottish team Rangers after failing to
OL,15,Fwin 12 of his first 17 games in charge.
OL,17,FHe got the job after he saw success at
OL,18,FSouthampton. Russell Martin led the
OL,19,Fteam to promotion to the Premier
OL,20,FLeague.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]
