OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FUnder his management, they went on a
OL,7,Fclub-record 25-game unbeaten run in
OL,8,Fthe Championship, secured a spot in
OL,9,Fthe playoffs, and beat Leeds United at
OL,10,FWembley.
OL,12,FDespite this success, he was sacked
OL,13,Fafter losing 13 of 16 Premier League
OL,14,Fgames.
OL,16,FHe left the club 20th in the table
OL,17,Fwith only five points after a 5-nil
OL,18,Floss to Tottenham Hotspur.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
