CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FBefore management, Martin played for
OL,7,F15 years as a defender, appearing for
OL,8,FWalsall and Peterborough. He spent
OL,9,Fmost of his career at Norwich and
OL,10,FWycombe Wanderers.
OL,12,FHe also made 29 appearances for
OL,13,FScotland at centre back.
OL,15,FRussell Martin is taking over the
OL,16,FLeicester City side after their shock
OL,17,Frelegation to League One.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
