CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FLeicester went down after sacking two
OL,7,Fmanagers, Marti Cifuentes and Gary
OL,8,FRowett, and suffering a six-point
OL,9,Fdeduction.
OL,11,FTheir relegation was made more
OL,12,Fshocking as it came on the 10-year
OL,13,Fanniversary of their unlikely Premier
OL,14,FLeague win.
OL,16,FThis means they join another unhappy
OL,17,Fclub with Blackburn Rovers and Leeds
OL,18,FUnited as the only teams to have
OL,19,Fplayed in both the Champions League
OL,20,Fand League One.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
