PN,34106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FMartin should be feeling confident, as
OL,7,Fthis Leicester City team will be one
OL,8,Fof the most expensive assembled squads
OL,9,Fto ever play in England's third tier.
OL,11,FThe squad that was relegated was worth
OL,12,Fan estimated #140 million.
OL,14,FMartin was credited during his time at
OL,15,FSouthampton for how he coached the
OL,16,Fteam to play. He likes his teams to
OL,17,Ffocus on keeping hold of the ball with
OL,18,Flots of short, accurate passing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
