CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1781556458
OL,3,CRussell Martin announced as the new
OL,4,CLeicester City manager
OL,6,FAs a manager, he also encourages hard
OL,7,Frunning, chasing down the opposition
OL,8,Fto avoid them having time to think.
OL,10,FLeicester City fans will be hoping
OL,11,Fhe'll bring some of the same magic he
OL,12,Fhad at Southampton to get them back
OL,13,Finto the Championship and, eventually,
OL,14,Fthe Premier League.
